{"tid":914208,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人覺得作曲家甚至填詞人地位應該要高過歌手","createTime":"2018-11-24T05:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T22:55:13.000Z","uid":128761,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"95fe58442e33ef6538766b7f4b1949fe0460960f","tid":914208,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"依家諗起某首流行曲，就只會記得係邊個唱<br />\n係咩人填詞？可能都會有人記下，但咩人作曲？根本冇人會記得<br />\n你講某首歌、某句歌詞，都會話係邊個邊個歌手唱<br />\n有冇人覺得作曲家、填詞人好慘？<br />\n<br />\n冇作曲家就冇歌手<br />\n但冇歌手都仲係可以有作曲家<br />\n而冇填詞人的話，歌手亦只能亨歌<br />\n偏偏依家搵錢最多既係歌手，而唔係作曲家、填詞人<br />\n<br />\n明明以前都係只會記作曲家，蕭邦呀...莫札特呀...<br />\n依家倒返轉真係幾可悲"},{"pid":"f322a3e47b74d42b384ae98ea27b08642873f1f8","tid":914208,"uid":104218,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳詠謙，人稱肥膏，樂壇大毒瘤<br />\n評價：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"f7c3596cdcda47a08ea2420c26b690fc89104090","tid":914208,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:38:10.000Z","msg":"係香港佢地討論價值同地位已經好高"},{"pid":"a79c83134bdcbaa859e77947ec94c64adef06820","tid":914208,"uid":37942,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"日本作曲家地位咪高"},{"pid":"bdcd7dfb4798242e707b3309c9bc7ebe63a479c6","tid":914208,"uid":37942,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"根本香港都冇樂壇"},{"pid":"de1652a397118be4649a84dc947a00b075ba5e50","tid":914208,"uid":64884,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"向來幕前都被幕後出名<br />\n歌如是電影亦如是電視亦如是"},{"pid":"b3a4c9ce9f9dce66fcc0bb158c95ad7c9e71b897","tid":914208,"uid":155902,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"仲有編曲果個, 編曲對首歌影響好大, 但偏偏無人理..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e953aa819960a37293d8988ee9932ae1809348","tid":914208,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得近年已經多咗人留意幕後<br />\n我聽歌都會睇下班底先"},{"pid":"c169b94dde422fc6b68bfcd3d36f547c9db0a0da","tid":914208,"uid":85682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"監製都重要，首歌要點樣去唱，用咩唱法，對首歌好大影響"},{"pid":"241109589185016833f4ffdd73564950d014abeb","tid":914208,"uid":159417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"其實以前歌唱家都可以去到天王巨星世界級，one god one farinelli 呢個程度，不過可能流傳後世有難度先無mozart 咁enduring 姐"},{"pid":"3725840002866dfaf0de54c2524b604ed089e43e","tid":914208,"uid":55800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T21:04:54.000Z","msg":"應該講，一首歌好聽，幕後班底功不可沒<br />\n但現實歸現實，你要啲人給予幕後班底同歌手同等甚至更多嘅注意係好難，因為首歌始終係歌手唱出黎，你就咁聽最容易留意到嘅的確係把人聲，至於曲/詞甚至編除非你好熟嗰個人嘅風格，否則都難啲辨認係出自何人之手，又唔係咁多人每聽一首歌都會去留意首歌係邊個班底嘅作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者咁講，就算一首作品再好聽，冇人唱其實首歌一樣唔會有人識，所以又唔可以話歌手係唔重要。當然歌手自己作曲就可以解決呢個問題，但世界係公平，出色嘅作曲人未必有好嘅歌喉或者好文彩，反之亦然。所以唱作歌手並唔多，先唯有分工合作。"},{"pid":"0ceef4dc819bce93c527387cc2c3097e7fc738b9","tid":914208,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79c83134bdcbaa859e77947ec94c64adef06820","tid":914208,"uid":37942,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:20:09.000Z",